* This is an automatically-generated screenshot database.
* 'screenshots' contains the actual, unscaled screenshots along with text
  files containing captions.
* 'thumbnails' contains automatically-scaled thumbnails generated from the
  previous folder
* Both a <script> and <noscript> section is generated, maximizing viewability
* jQuery is used in the scripted version
* The generated file is 'screenshots.html'
* The 'build' script does all of the work
* 'build' requires ImageMagick
